              <para>
                <text>A QFE that fails to comply with a direction of the Commission given under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1282638" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1637401 - prov 73" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1637637" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 73(3)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="785483" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1637637" atidlm:targetKey="13496411" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM1584717" atidlm:targetName="prov 73" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1637637" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1584705.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1584768.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1584791" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> commits an offence and is liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding $25,000.</text>
