        <prov id="DLM1584792" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">133</label>
          <heading>Offence of failing to comply with obligations in relation to authorised financial advisers</heading>
          <prov.body>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
              <para>
                <text>A QFE that contravenes <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1282639" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1637402 - prov 76" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1637638" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 76(1)(c)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="785484" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1637638" atidlm:targetKey="13496416" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM1584722" atidlm:targetName="prov 76" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1637638" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1584705.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1584768.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1584792" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> commits an offence and is liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding $50,000.</text>
              </para>
            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
              <para>
                <text>It is a defence to a charge under <citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (1)</citation> that a QFE has contravened <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1282640" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1637403 - prov 76" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1637639" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 76(1)(c)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="785485" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1637639" atidlm:targetKey="13496416" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM1584722" atidlm:targetName="prov 76" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1637639" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1584705.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1584768.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1584792" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> if the QFE proves on a balance of probabilities that the QFE believed on reasonable grounds that the financial adviser in question did not perform a financial adviser service that only an authorised financial adviser may perform.</text>
              </para>
            </subprov>
          </prov.body>
        </prov>
        <prov id="DLM1584793" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
